ExtensionFactory的injectExtension()方法内，如果存在setter注入，则通过getSetterProperty取得setter的驼峰名称后传入
```
private T injectExtension(T instance) {
        try {
            if (objectFactory != null) {
                for (Method method : instance.getClass().getMethods()) {
                    if (isSetter(method)) {
                        /**
                         * Check {@link DisableInject} to see if we need auto injection for this property
                         */
                        if (method.getAnnotation(DisableInject.class) != null) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        Class<?> pt = method.getParameterTypes()[0];
                        if (ReflectUtils.isPrimitives(pt)) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        try {
                            String property = getSetterProperty(method);
                            Object object = objectFactory.getExtension(pt, property);
                            if (object != null) {
                                method.invoke(instance, object);
                            }
                        } catch (Exception e) {
                            logger.error("Failed to inject via method " + method.getName()
                                    + " of interface " + type.getName() + ": " + e.getMessage(), e);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        } catch (Exception e) {
            logger.error(e.getMessage(), e);
        }
        return instance;
    }
```
既然已经使用了setter来注入，是否可以虑通过setter的name来查找具体需要的Extension来注入。防止依赖自身，也可以考虑增加name的同名限制约定

也可以通过判断方法上标注的@adaptive来达到自适应注入。获取setter方法后，在根据方法上的@adaptive来调用createAdaptiveExtensionClass()方法生成代理实例
```
private T injectExtension(T instance) {
        try {
            if (objectFactory != null) {
                for (Method method : instance.getClass().getMethods()) {
                    if (isSetter(method)) {
                        /**
                         * Check {@link DisableInject} to see if we need auto injection for this property
                         */
                        if (method.getAnnotation(DisableInject.class) != null) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        //在此对@Adaptive做处理，然后通过AdaptiveClassCodeGenerator类来生成代理类，并实例化
                        Class<?> pt = method.getParameterTypes()[0];
                        if (ReflectUtils.isPrimitives(pt)) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        try {
                            String property = getSetterProperty(method);
                            Object object = objectFactory.getExtension(pt, property);
                            if (object != null) {
                                method.invoke(instance, object);
                            }
                        } catch (Exception e) {
                            logger.error("Failed to inject via method " + method.getName()
                                    + " of interface " + type.getName() + ": " + e.getMessage(), e);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        } catch (Exception e) {
            logger.error(e.getMessage(), e);
        }
        return instance;
    }
```

